{"tid":1533543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再繼續咁隨性行動，隨時會輸","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:17:37.000Z","uid":258003,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1525f32a837f0e861e4e3e90d6d4f37b5be3d7d0","tid":1533543,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:51:41.000Z","msg":"我明白各位對狗隻有非常大嘅怨念，但係可唔可以唔好鋪鋪都圍狗屋咁dry呢<br />\n就算真係圍狗屋，狗仔一出門口容乜易就可以捉到你哋啦，點解永遠都要陣地戰呢，能力懸殊果種係咪應該游擊<br />\n用返老毛果套<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵進我退 <br />\n敵駐我擾 <br />\n敵疲我打 <br />\n敵退我追</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家第一點都做唔到，&ldquo;敵進&rdquo;咗我地成日都照鬧狗，唔退，搞到好多手足俾狗咬傷、捉<br />\n所以要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一抵達已經做好散水準備</span></span><br />\n到時狗出到黎即就唔好糾纏，即刻散！<br />\n同埋每區不宜過多街坊參與，過多只會導致走唔切，有傷、捉風險。<br />\n試下&ldquo;真撚狗&rdquo;，收到風狗仔出到黎或者有其他狗過緊黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，即走返屋企或者遠離該地<br />\n隔多幾個鐘等狗番晒去，再repeat步驟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者積累怒氣，星期六日先開大技<br />\n好處如下：<br />\n減少傷亡<br />\n人數集中<br />\n對狗威脅較大<br />\n<br />\n唔好無聊就撚狗啦，唔少手足被捉，果區嘅街坊怕咗就唔敢出黎被滅聲，例如深水埗黃大仙。<br />\n勇武手足捉吓一個好快冇晒，抗爭本錢亦一直削弱緊。"},{"pid":"5f9c404efaaa70e11c09e0caabf1633b4f8286ae","tid":1533543,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:54:36.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f9d4c2686420228557e7f4d4c70c92f5f1b4925","tid":1533543,"uid":179718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"其實真係好唔明<br />\n呢家成隊犬一出狗屋5分鐘內就會鳩衝捉人<br />\n點解係都要撚到人地鳩衝先散，係對自己賽跑有信心定咩？<br />\n<br />\n呢家真係好唔想睇直播，因為一定有手足俾人拉，個心好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0187d70cd8f41f6c23e7b1a998f03677bd8bcc2e","tid":1533543,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5495dc0be42e46998bf05a6bad83c01d4413f561","tid":1533543,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"P牌好似推唔郁？<br />\n唔知呢<br />\n都要試！<br />\n希望多啲手足睇到"},{"pid":"3a0cd81450ac7560691c8c12659919e0d253b656","tid":1533543,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:15:59.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"706a4a656b165620d1718226fa3d589e4e5fffe7","tid":1533543,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"5b014c72737f3e43e6a0f82b129e3a480b17943c","tid":1533543,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:16:21.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"9a57140f84cb9dec45b1d264523a607adee612f1","tid":1533543,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"6c1a6a5c9a90e13f123cb59284ea7257ce20dee4","tid":1533543,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:16:41.0